data.description: Situated in the picturesque Conway locale, a welcoming house reveals itself on over 1/2 acre lot, inviting you to explore its enchanting allure and make it your own personal haven.  Warm and inviting, this spacious home features a beamed ceiling that adds character and charm. Spread over a generous 2847 square feet, the property offers ample living space and comfort for its residents. With four bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, this home provides ample space for comfortable living.  This beautiful property boasts a lovely lawn and an  in-ground swimming pool, perfect for outdoor relaxation and fun activities. The home also features a carport, providing added convenience and security. Enjoy the best of indoor and outdoor living with this lovely home.
